cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper involves reinforcement learning algorithms and transfer learning in the context of robotic manipulation skills. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of invariant feature spaces, which suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with the transfer of skills between different robots, which could potentially fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
